  Description: "You\u2019re fully immersed in another ancestry\u2019s culture and
    traditions, whether born into them, earned through rite of passage, or bonded
    through a deep friendship or romance. Choose a common ancestry or another ancestry
    to which you have access. You can select ancestry feats from the ancestry you
    chose, in addition to your character\u2019s own ancestry, as long as the ancestry
    feats don\u2019t require any physiological feature that you lack, as determined
    by the GM."
